Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.91,0:23:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日怎樣有意義地度過？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼代替她？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}{\fad(500,700)}{\bord1}{\3c&H000000&}後期：Tsurugi
